## Clone Database from Production

```bash
# 1. Export from production
ssh -p 65002 u803853690@82.25.82.111 "cd /home/u803853690/domains/deetech.cc/public_html/uffizi/backend && mysqldump -u u803853690_uffizi -pPROD_PASSWORD u803853690_uffizi_tickets > backup.sql"

# 2. Download
scp -P 65002 u803853690@82.25.82.111:/home/u803853690/domains/deetech.cc/public_html/uffizi/backend/backup.sql ./

# 3. Clean and import
tail -n +3 backup.sql > backup_clean.sql
"C:/Program Files/MySQL/MySQL Server 8.0/bin/mysql.exe" -u root -pYOUR_PASSWORD uffizi_tickets < backup_clean.sql
```

