## Quick Start Commands

```bash
# Start backend
cd D:/Uffizi-Ticket-App/backend
php artisan serve --host=127.0.0.1 --port=8000

# Start frontend (new terminal)
cd D:/Uffizi-Ticket-App/frontend
npm run dev -- --port 5173 --host 127.0.0.1
```

